{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000000", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000000.wav", "transcript": "todas las tardes a la hora del t\u00e9 se acordaban siempre del loro y recordaban tambi\u00e9n cu\u00e1nto le gustaba comer pan mojado en t\u00e9 con leche pobre pedrito nunca m\u00e1s lo ver\u00edan porque hab\u00eda muerto", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 15.01, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000000.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 418.49, "segment_end_sec": 433.5}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000001", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000001.wav", "transcript": "ahora bien en medio de esta felicidad sucedi\u00f3 que una tarde de lluvia sali\u00f3 por fin el sol despu\u00e9s de cinco d\u00edas de temporal y pedrito se puso a volar gritando qu\u00e9 lindo d\u00eda lorito", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 12.79, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000001.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 147.8, "segment_end_sec": 160.59}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000002", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000002.wav", "transcript": "le gustaba tambi\u00e9n burlarse de las gallinas a las cuatro o cinco de la tarde que era la hora en que tomaban el t\u00e9 en la casa el loro entraba tambi\u00e9n en el comedor y se sub\u00eda por el mantel a comer pan mojado en leche ten\u00eda locura por el t\u00e9 con leche", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 15.79, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000002.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 88.3, "segment_end_sec": 104.09}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000003", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000003.wav", "transcript": "vivieron en adelante muy contentos pero el loro no se olvidaba de lo que le hab\u00eda hecho el tigre y todas las tardes cuando entraba en el comedor para tomar el t\u00e9 se acercaba siempre a la piel del tigre tendida delante de la estufa y lo invitaba a tomar t\u00e9 con leche", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 15.46, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000003.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 711.3, "segment_end_sec": 726.76}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000004", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000004.wav", "transcript": "pero pedrito no hab\u00eda muerto sino que continuaba en su cueva sin dejarse ver por nadie porque sent\u00eda mucha verg\u00fcenza de verse pelado como un rat\u00f3n de noche bajaba a comer y sub\u00eda enseguida", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 12.95, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000004.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 433.5, "segment_end_sec": 446.45}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000005", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000005.wav", "transcript": "rica papa en casa repiti\u00f3 gritando cuanto pod\u00eda m\u00e1s cerca no oigo respondi\u00f3 el tigre con su voz ronca", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 11.36, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000005.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 292.89, "segment_end_sec": 304.25}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000006", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000006.wav", "transcript": "y volviendo a entrar en la casa para tomar la escopeta emprendi\u00f3 junto con pedrito el viaje al paraguay convinieron en que cuando pedrito viera al tigre lo distraer\u00eda charlando para que el hombre pudiera acercarse despacito con la escopeta y as\u00ed pas\u00f3 el loro", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 16.06, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000006.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 528.18, "segment_end_sec": 544.24}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000007", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000007.wav", "transcript": "pero entretanto en el comedor todos extra\u00f1aban su ausencia d\u00f3nde estar\u00e1 pedrito dec\u00edan y llamaban pedrito rica papa pedrito t\u00e9 con leche pedrito pero pedrito no se mov\u00eda de su cueva ni respond\u00eda nada mudo y quieto", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 17.32, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000007.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 390.66, "segment_end_sec": 407.98}}
{"sample_id": "10667_6706_000008", "audio_path": "../imported/mls_spanish_test_subset/10667_6706_000008.wav", "transcript": "y he aqu\u00ed que de pronto vio brillar en el suelo a trav\u00e9s de las ramas dos luces verdes como enormes bichos de luz qu\u00e9 ser\u00e1 se dijo el loro", "language": "es-ES", "duration_sec": 13.44, "split": "test", "tags": ["external", "mls", "spanish", "audiobook", "read_speech", "subset"], "metadata": {"source": "Multilingual LibriSpeech", "source_ref": "facebook/multilingual_librispeech mls_spanish test", "source_url": "https://huggingface.co/datasets/facebook/multilingual_librispeech", "license": "CC BY 4.0", "acoustic_profile": "multilingual_audiobook", "audio_format": "wav", "original_format": "flac", "original_member": "10667_6706_000008.flac", "source_audio_url": "http://www.archive.org/download/cuentosdelaselva_1603_librivox/cuentosdelaselva_06_quiroga_64kb.mp3", "segment_start_sec": 176.6, "segment_end_sec": 190.04}}
